00:09:53,373 --> 00:10:19,023
for this evening's program is probably overdue. Our very gracious and admittedly last-minute guests are by no means strangers, but you don't always get to see them in this particular light. Please say hello to WMCC Executive Director Lisa Crossman, the queenly wave, and Board President Melinda Walsh-Reagan,

