36
00:18:28,212 --> 00:18:53,710
and I turned down something that I couldn't believe I was turning down, but it was just like, they didn't meet me where I needed them to meet me, and I didn't know what I was gonna do, and then here comes Steven, pulling through the door, and here comes this opportunity, and it started out as just a board opportunity, but some things had gone on in the organization, and the executive director had,

