00:20:58,923 --> 00:21:24,640
I tell you, I would go nowhere else that length of a ride other than Medford because I could say, I leave my house every day and I go home. And especially being in West Medford where I've been in that office now for about 11 years. And the amazing thing was that for many people who walked through the door, I could say, I went to school with you or your kids.

44
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:52,940
And there have just been so many amazing stories I've heard from people coming through to talk. So, like, there's something about Medford that just always pulls you home, and I've always felt very much at home here in West Medford. It's really interesting that you mention how you came from your area of Medford to the Hervey School, because 10 years before Boston got into the kerfluff that they got into about busing,

