00:21:53,682 --> 00:22:18,269
Medford parents voluntarily allowed their kids from the Hervey to be bused to the Gleason, the Waite, and the Dame school to help them achieve racial balance. And it was the first community in Massachusetts that would allow that to happen, where the parents volunteered to let their kids go to these other schools. So it's kind of an interesting paradox.

46
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:27,787
Okay, very good. Now, your bank recently changed brands and management. How has that impacted your role as a branch manager?

