48
00:22:56,373 --> 00:23:22,867
storming, the changes upon you, and then you get into norming, where it's normalizing. I think we're getting there now. And then performing, so soon to come, performing. Yeah, that's training talk, you know, that storming, norming, performing thing. I used to hear about that quite a lot. So Lisa, I wanna ask you about Grant, okay? Because as he, when you came in the door, he came in the door with you.

