It's amazing. Like I said, my family had a business, so I was always with my parents at work. That's how I understand business and things like that. So it's amazing to have him with me and have that same experience and pass that on to him. But being here, I always tell the story about when we went to Florida, and when we were visiting my mom,

51
00:24:02,371 --> 00:24:23,228
It was a senior community and he was the only child and he went down to the pool I let him go with his great aunt and they said Lisa Grant made so many friends He was chatting up all the seniors and they just loved him. And so I love that he

52
00:24:23,701 --> 00:24:51,207
